Server.start()
  → load ServerConfig
  → EventLoop.run()

EventLoop detects new connection
  → ClientConnection created

ClientConnection reads → HttpRequest + HttpResponse

ServerPipeline.processRequest(ServerConfig, req, res):
  → SessionManager.ensure_session()
    → TimeUtil, RandomUtil
  → RateLimiter.allow()
    → TokenBucket, TimeUtil
  → Router.resolve()
    → RouteResolver
      → Location, VirtualServer
    → select Handler:
        - StaticHandler → PathUtil
        - PutPatchHandler → PathUtil, ETagUtil, CRC32
        - ProxyHandler → ReverseProxy, Balancer, UpstreamPool, Upstream
        - CgiHandler → CgiRegistry, CgiProcess
  → Handler fills HttpResponse
  → Logger records event

ClientConnection writes HttpResponse → close or keep-alive


12) Acceptance Checklists (Definition of Done)
	Per feature:

	Unit tests ≥90% critical paths.

	Integration tests cover success + 3 edge cases.

	Handles timeouts/errors gracefully.

	No leaks under Valgrind; clean ASan/UBSan.

	Throughput & latency not regressed vs previous tag.


